The following command will update all the packages to the latest minor version
npm update --save

To update single package on the command line, run the following command:
npm update <module> --save

To update dev package on the command line, run the following command:
npm update --dev --save -dev

To update all global packages on the command line, run the following command:
npm update -g

To update single global package on the command line, run the following command:
npm update -g <module>
